Jamie Torode,aged7: It is Sunday.Igot up very early to see my baby cousin get christened.We learnt a song.It was called 'The Lord is my Shepherd'.After that Iwent to my Nana's.I had my dinner there. We had roast chicken,peas,roast potatoes and gravy.For afters, it was very nice cakes.All the children in my class have roast dinners on Sundays.
